RabbitVCS is a set of graphical tools written to provide simple and straightforward access to the version control 
systems you use. We currently support Subversion and Git on a variety of clients such as Nautilus, Thunar, Nemo, 
Caja, and on the command line.

Optional: 

thunarx-python for Thunar support
*python2-nautilus for Nautilus3 (DLG,..) support
meld recommend for graphical diff tool support
